{"tid":1348270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 唔好中計！","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:21:23.000Z","uid":264584,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"237cfbbec29e7f596a41161a7dced1cb0d1f6ded","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"政府用白色恐怖都嚇香港人唔到<br />\n就用啲下三濫嘅手段 <br />\n搵黑社會幫手<br />\n一黎轉移視線<br />\n二黎等市民人心惶惶 渴望穩定<br />\n三黎就等群眾鬥群眾<br />\n<br />\n我地可以嬲<br />\n可以覺得憤慨<br />\n但絕對唔可以驚<br />\n絕對唔可以俾政府spin到<br />\n<br />\n搞到今日咁嘅局面<br />\n係因為政府唔肯回應五大訴求<br />\n我地要全民勇武<br />\n繼續將矛盾指返政府<br />\n再將佢啲手手腳腳逐隻剝走<br />\n建制派 黑警 紅媒 黑社會 <br />\n一個都唔可以放過"},{"pid":"4060f52ad599627b256b9ceb3f655cb94f84b37b","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"香港人 頂住啊 退無可退啦！"},{"pid":"f097f68460046c0d46744aeec7d8960b015edc23","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"退無可退 全民勇武"},{"pid":"0371f8a0de8299da5077f5c3a73b7bda16269646","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"退無可退 全民勇武"},{"pid":"3b57a5fc9d5ea85592b357b4d12ee5ea17ae6171","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c0f45634023694a8f9ff923f3dfedf33cc6c945","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79d73c4648cd11fed749d810cd00de152962eee5","tid":1348270,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14d306957af0a28005d25c67d1e4b5b19da044a2","tid":1348270,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzDogu0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi